  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON:  The change of use to residential would be unacceptable in terms of housing standards involving a single aspect unit with the basement bedroom outlook very restricted due to the deep and short lightwell., a floor area of only 35 sq metres, a front garden also below the DM stadard for ground floor units at only 12 sq metres and apparently inaccurate drawings indicating that the site area is to a greater width than is the case.  The accommodation would be contrary to the London Plan 2011, policies D3, H3, H7 and H10 of the Unitary Development Plan 2002, policy CS9 of the Core Strategy 2011, and policies DM1, DM12 and DM13 of the emerging Development Management policies, submission June 2012."
